headline: DailyPay Appoints Accomplished Technology and Product Leader Poulomi Damany As Chief Product Officer
summary: DailyPay, the leading On-Demand Pay platform and financial wellness solution, has appointed Poulomi Damany as its Chief Product Officer where she will be responsible for unifying and optimizing our product segment at DailyPay. Damany will report to Stacy Greiner, Chief Executive Officer, DailyPay.
